nts in Wisconsin.','https://www.google.com/maps/place/Rib+Mountain+State+Park/@44.921581,-89.6907959,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x8800221c8f0eb50f:0xbca085bc477383cc!8m2!3d44.921581!4d-89.688221!16zL20vMGg2MGRs?entry=ttu','149801 State Park Rd, Wausau, WI 54401',0,1,NULL,NULL),(70,'Richard Bong State Recreation Area','Kenosha','Supports recreational activities, including ATVs, falconry, hunting and sled dog training, and model aircraft on the site of the abortive R.I. Bong Air Force Base.','https://www.google.com/maps/place/Richard+Bong+State+Recreation+Area/@42.6324934,-88.129873,16.9z/data=!4m6!3m5!1s0x8805791e53bec5b1:0x471fc7582f7b3283!8m2!3d42.6352374!4d-88.1274875!16zL20vMDEybHQ4?entry=ttu','26313 Burlington Rd, Kansasville, WI 53139',1,1,NULL,NULL),(71,'Roche-a-Cri State Park','Adams','Contains a 300-foot (91 m) outcropping bearing the NRHP-listed Roche-a-Cri Petroglyphs.','https://www.google.com/maps/place/Roche-A-Cri+State+Park/@44.0012338,-89.8152209,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x8800bb73a7bb06bb:0xabc61e99a07ac951!8m2!3d44.0012338!4d-89.812646!16zL20vMGcxZHZz?entry=ttu','1767 WI-13 Trunk, Friendship, WI 53934',1,1,NULL,NULL),(72,'Rock Island State Park','Door','Encompasses most of vehicle-free Rock Island, accessed by two ferry rides at the tip of the Door Peninsula. Four listings are on the NRHP, including the 1836 Pottawatomie Lighthouse and inventor Chester Thordarson\'s 20th-century estate.','https://www.google.com/maps/place/Rock+Island+State+Park/@45.4147805,-86.8204385,16.91z/data=!4m6!3m5!1s0x4d4cfd2570c03c53:0x8295b761e8c2093e!8m2!3d45.4147892!4d-86.8181649!16zL20vMDVmc201?entry=ttu','1924 Indian Point Rd, Washington, WI 54246',1,1,NULL,NULL),(73,'Rocky Arbor State Park','Juneau','Preserves sandstone outcroppings similar to the nearby Dells of the Wisconsin River along one of the river\'s former channels.','https://www.google.com/maps/place/Rocky+Arbor+State+Park/@43.6389009,-89.8064035,15.53z/data=!4m6!3m5!1s0x88074f86c7577dc5:0x5adb29546c480bf